	keywords = {话语分析, 经济绩效, 企业社会责任信息披露, 语义分析 Corporate Social Responsibility Information Disclosure, 元分析, 中国上市公司, Chinese Listed Companies, Corporate Economic Performance, Discourse Analysis, Meta-analysis, Semantic Analysis},
	file = {企业社会责任信息披露与经济绩效关系研究_刘智宇.pdf:/Users/chendongyu/Zotero/storage/UVW2ACIL/企业社会责任信息披露与经济绩效关系研究_刘智宇.pdf:application/pdf},
